  "description": "<h1><strong>🥐 Passion Is Our Main Ingredient🥐</strong></h1><p><strong>Baker & Cook Singapore </strong>- Singapore’s only true artisan bakery & foodstore is hiring!</p><h3>💰 <strong>** Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</strong>💰</h3><p>✅ Singaporean* | Singapore PR* | PLOC</p><p>✅ 6 OFF per month</p><p>🚫 No quota available</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>🍕 Outlets: Asian Civilizations Museum</strong>|<strong>Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Guoco Midtown) | Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Jewel) | Chip Bee Garden | Dairy Farm | Dempsey | Eng Kong Park | Hillcrest | Namly Place | South Bouna Vista | Serangoon Garden | Swan Lake | Sunset Way</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Assisting the Executive Chef/ Head Chef with daily operations</li><li>Overseeing at least 3 outlets in terms of daily operations, training, ordering, food wastage control, etc</li><li>Ensure proper opening and/or closing of the ktichen while adhering to Company SOP</li><li>Maintain a high standard of cleanliness within the kitchen and strictly abide with health/sanitation regulations</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties base on operational needs</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Certificate in Culinary Skills or its equivalent</li><li>Minimum 2 years supervisory experience in a kitchen specialising in Western cuisine (Pizza, Pasta, etc)</li><li>Good team player and self-motivated</li><li>6 OFF days per month</li><li>Able to work on weekends/public holidays</li><li>Split shift required</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Various allowances**</li><li>Medical + Dental benefits</li><li>Birthday vouchers</li><li>Staff discounts across brands</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested party may apply via https://forms.gle/G1q4e4nDrfW1yDmL7</p><p>** T&C applies</p>",
